snippet.title: Destiny: Rise of Iron - PlayStation Experience 2016: The Dawning Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/destiny-2/?emcid=or-1s-412983

Celebrate your Light when The Dawning arrives on December 13th. Compete on new tracks with the return of Sparrow Racing League, challenge your skills and set records in the all new Vanguard Elite Strike Scoring, and earn a new arsenal of weapons and gear.  

Exclusively on Destiny: Rise of Iron, available now: https://www.destinythegame.com/wheret...

FOLLOW DESTINY:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DestinyTheGame
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/destinythegame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/destinythegame

FOLLOW BUNGIE:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Bungie/
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/bungie
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bungie/

Requires Destiny Game and the Taken King. (Includes Expansions I & II) Sold separately. Some content shown also availabe in the Eververse Store.
